
1.  Whenever a new post is to be added please keep in mind the following points :

    a) Decide under which category the post falls under. currently we have general,technical,philosophy
    b) once decided please go to the respective folder under the 'html' directory and place it under the 'posts' directory.

2.  Inside the 'posts directory' you will find the html files named according to a naming order. Please follow it 
    
    a) Naming convetion is 'sequenceNumberOfYourPost.html'.

